Package: IBclust
Type: Package
Title: Deterministic Information Bottleneck Method for Clustering
        Mixed-Type Data
Version: 1.2
Author: Efthymios Costa, Ioanna Papatsouma, Angelos Markos
Maintainer: Angelos Markos <amarkos@eled.duth.gr>
Description: Implements the Deterministic Information Bottleneck method for clustering datasets with both categorical and continuous variables. The package handles data preprocessing, feature selection, and clustering optimization using information-theoretic approaches <doi:10.48550/arXiv.2407.03389>. 
